DataElement.preferredName: Fatigue Severity Scale Past Week Exercise Brings on Fatigue Agreement Score 7 Point Scale
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A person's stated observation of their agreement with a statement about exercise bringing on their fatigue in the past week, using a seven point Likert scale.
